Pay attention to grapefruit, orange and apple juice.
These drinks, consumed especially in the summer because they are thirst-quenching and rich in vitamins, if combined with certain vital drugs, alter the absorption amplifying or decreasing depending on the case, their effectiveness, with even serious consequences for health.
