According to experts, even orange and apple juice contains substances that inhibit drugs.
Long is the list of active ingredients inhibited by grapefruit and other juices.
From there, the appeal of Michele Carruba, director of the pharmacology department of the Public University of Milan: "These discoveries are generally, immediately reported to the various national and international drug agencies that will have to change the informative notes of the drugs if necessary.
